This matter is reset.
Final pre-trial scheduled for January 13, 2023 at 09:00 am.

ADDRESS INFO for Travis L Mojeck
Current: 623 SUPERIOR AVENUE, Sheboygan, WI 53081 United States  (Effective: 10-21-2022)
Prior: 1504 Illinois Ave, Sheboygan, WI 53081

9:03 AM Defendant Travis L Mojeck in court.  Attorney Jennifer C Zima in court for State of Wisconsin.  Attorney Aaron Thomas Vruwink in court for Travis L Mojeck. 
Officer T is sworn in and testifies. Testifies to being an Officer with the Marshfield Police Department. Testifies to reviewing a report from Officer Fox. Testifies to that Officer being dispatched to a parking lot for a woman acting strange. Testifies to the Officer going to the location and speaking with SMA, whom stated it was her daughter they saw outside, not her. Testifies to the Rachel stating the substances that she was under the influence of. Testifies to SMA consenting to a K9 sniff of the apartment. Testifies to the substances and paraphernalia that was found. Testifies to the substances being tested and the results. Witness identifies Rachel and Travis in court, court recognizes.

Court finds probable cause to believe a felony was committed and the defendants committed them.

Bond is continued.
Final pre-trial scheduled for October 21, 2022 at 09:00 am.
